sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/ODH Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as kserve-webhook-server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant Controller as kserve-controller-manager<br/>Watch K8s API
    participant Storage as S3/GCS/Azure Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Activator as Knative Activator<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Predictor as Model Server (Predictor)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Transformer as Transformer Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Explainer as Explainer Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS

    Note over User,Controller: Flow 1: InferenceService Creation and Deployment
    User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService CR<br/>POST /apis/serving.kserve.io/v1beta1<br/>Bearer Token (OAuth)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate InferenceService<br/>mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validated/Mutated Resource
    K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService Created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceService<br/>Service Account Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Knative Service/Deployment<br/>Create VirtualService<br/>Service Account Token
    Note over Storage,Predictor: Storage Initializer (Init Container)
    Predictor->>Storage: Download Model Artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>AWS IAM/GCP SA/Azure Creds
    Storage-->>Predictor: Model Files (shared volume)

    Note over User,Predictor: Flow 2: Inference Request (Serverless Mode)
    User->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Bearer Token/None
    Gateway->>Activator: Forward Request<br/>HTTP/80 mTLS<br/>Service Identity
    Activator->>Predictor: Inference Request<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
    Predictor-->>Activator: Prediction Result
    Activator-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over User,Explainer: Flow 3: Inference with Transformer and Explainer
    User->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
    Gateway->>Transformer: Pre-process Request<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
    Transformer->>Predictor: Transformed Input<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
    Predictor-->>Transformer: Prediction
    Transformer-->>Gateway: Post-processed Response
    Gateway-->>User: HTTPS/443

    User->>Gateway: GET /v1/models/model:explain<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
    Gateway->>Explainer: Explanation Request<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
    Explainer->>Predictor: Get Prediction<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
    Predictor-->>Explainer: Prediction Result
    Explainer-->>Gateway: Explanation + Prediction<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
    Gateway-->>User: HTTPS/443
